          <fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  A \to  B]]></fr:tex> be <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-000U.xml" title="Biinverse" addr="//erct/erct-000U" type="local">biinvertible</fr:link>; then for any type <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[C]]></fr:tex>, the postcomposition map <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen f\circ  -\right \rparen \mathclose {}
\colon  
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen C\to  A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
\to  
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen C\to  B\right \rparen \mathclose {}
]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-000U.xml" title="Biinverse" addr="//erct/erct-000U" type="local">biinvertible</fr:link>.</fr:p>
 
   
